{File:FXI_IS.txt  Index:25  Index Date:20170524  PL:83.33%  PS:16.67%  Trades:6  CL:1}

IF CLOSE OF 2 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 0 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 0 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 6 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 6 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 3 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 3 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 4 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 4 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 5 BARS AGO
THEN BUY NEXT BAR ON THE OPEN WITH
PROFIT TARGET AT ENTRY PRICE + 1.6964106 %
AND STOP LOSS AT ENTRY PRICE - 1.6020506 %
